<paragraph blockId="16.[160,1156,1494,1728]" box="[160,480,1494,1520]" pageId="16" pageNumber="2854">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[160,480,1494,1520]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="2854">Justification of the transfer</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="16.[160,1156,1494,1728]" lastBlockId="17.[160,1155,142,271]" lastPageId="17" lastPageNumber="2855" pageId="16" pageNumber="2854">
<bibRefCitation author="Patel SK" box="[160,292,1530,1555]" pageId="16" pageNumber="2854" pagination="44 - 46" refId="ref7664" refString="Patel SK. 1988. A new species of spider of the genus: Sergiolus (Gnaphosidae) from India. Biol Bull India. 10: 44 - 46." type="journal article" year="1988">Patel (1988)</bibRefCitation>
described 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Patel" authorityYear="1988" box="[414,548,1530,1555]" class="Arachnida" family="Gnaphosidae" genus="Sergiolus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="16" pageNumber="2854" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="khodiarae">
<emphasis box="[414,548,1530,1555]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="2854">S. khodiarae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
based on a 
<typeStatus box="[683,783,1530,1555]" pageId="16" pageNumber="2854">holotype</typeStatus>
female collected in 
<collectingRegion box="[1007,1091,1530,1555]" country="India" name="Gujarat" pageId="16" pageNumber="2854">Gujarat</collectingRegion>
. Even though we were unable to examine the type specimen of this species, which is presumably lost, the original illustrations of the epigyne of this species show that it lacks diagnostic features of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Simon" authorityYear="1892" box="[409,506,1634,1659]" class="Arachnida" family="Gnaphosidae" genus="Sergiolus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="16" pageNumber="2854" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[409,506,1634,1659]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="2854">Sergiolus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(see previous paragraph on 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Sankaran &amp; Caleb &amp; Sebastian" authorityYear="2021" baseAuthorityName="Sankaran &amp; Caleb &amp; Sebastian" baseAuthorityYear="2021" box="[826,1048,1634,1659]" class="Arachnida" family="Gnaphosidae" genus="Sergiolus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="16" pageNumber="2854" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="lamhetaghatensis">
<emphasis box="[826,1048,1634,1659]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="2854">H. lamhetaghatensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
); instead, it resembles the species of 
<taxonomicName authority="Westring, 1874" authorityName="Westring" authorityYear="1874" box="[479,798,1669,1694]" class="Arachnida" family="Gnaphosidae" genus="Poecilochroa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="16" pageNumber="2854" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[479,618,1669,1694]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="2854">Poecilochroa</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Westring N" box="[628,798,1669,1694]" pageId="16" pageNumber="2854" pagination="1 - 68" refId="ref8151" refString="Westring N. 1874. Bemerkungen uber die Arachnologischen Abhandlungen von Dr T. Thorell unter dem Titel: 1 °, On European Spiders, pts 1 et 2, Upsala, 1869 - 70. 2 °, Remarks on Synonyms of European Spiders, Upsala, 1872 - 73. Goteborgs Kungliga Vetenskaps och Vitterhets Samhalles Handlingar 14: 1 - 68." type="journal article" year="1874">Westring, 1874</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
as illustrated for 
<taxonomicName authority="(Tikader, 1982)" baseAuthorityName="Tikader" baseAuthorityYear="1982" class="Arachnida" family="Gnaphosidae" genus="Sergiolus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="16" pageNumber="2854" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="poonaensis">
<emphasis box="[1004,1155,1669,1694]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="2854">P. poonaensis</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Tikader BK" box="[166,317,1703,1728]" pageId="16" pageNumber="2854" pagination="295 - 536" refId="ref8093" refString="Tikader BK. 1982. Family Gnaphosidae. Fauna India (Araneae). 3: 295 - 536." type="journal article" year="1982">Tikader, 1982</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authority="Paik, 1992" authorityName="Paik" authorityYear="1992" box="[380,640,1703,1728]" class="Arachnida" family="Gnaphosidae" genus="Poecilochroa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="16" pageNumber="2854" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="taeguensis">
<emphasis box="[380,521,1703,1728]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="2854">P. taeguensis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Paik KY" box="[527,640,1703,1728]" pageId="16" pageNumber="2854" pagination="117 - 130" refId="ref7635" refString="Paik KY. 1992. Three new species of the genus Poecilochroa (Araneae: Gnaphosidae) from Korea. Korean Arachnol. 7: 117 - 130." type="journal article" year="1992">Paik, 1992</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
: epigyne with a median depression and large, bean-like spermathecae (compare 
<bibRefCitation author="Patel SK" box="[559,680,142,167]" pageId="17" pageNumber="2855" pagination="44 - 46" refId="ref7664" refString="Patel SK. 1988. A new species of spider of the genus: Sergiolus (Gnaphosidae) from India. Biol Bull India. 10: 44 - 46." type="journal article" year="1988">Patel 1988</bibRefCitation>
, fig 1c–d with 
<bibRefCitation author="Chatzaki M &amp; Thaler K &amp; Mylonas M" box="[859,1100,142,167]" pageId="17" pageNumber="2855" pagination="559 - 601" refId="ref7044" refString="Chatzaki M, Thaler K, Mylonas M. 2002 a. Ground spiders (Gnaphosidae; Araneae) of Crete (Greece). Taxonomy and distribution. I. Rev Suisse Zool. 109: 559 - 601. doi: 10.5962 / bhl. part. 79611." type="journal article" year="2002">Chatzaki et al. 2002a</bibRefCitation>
, figs 10–11; 
<bibRefCitation author="Lissner J &amp; Chatzaki M" box="[246,553,177,202]" pageId="17" pageNumber="2855" pagination="16 - 21" refId="ref7550" refString="Lissner J, Chatzaki M. 2016. First records of Poecilochroa taborensis Levy, 1999 (Araneae: Gnaphosidae) from Greece and Cyprus with notes on some closely related species. Nieuwsbrief SPINED. 36: 16 - 21." type="journal article" year="2016">Lissner and Chatzaki 2016</bibRefCitation>
, fig. 4A–D; 
<bibRefCitation author="Paik KY" box="[697,810,177,202]" pageId="17" pageNumber="2855" pagination="117 - 130" refId="ref7635" refString="Paik KY. 1992. Three new species of the genus Poecilochroa (Araneae: Gnaphosidae) from Korea. Korean Arachnol. 7: 117 - 130." type="journal article" year="1992">Paik 1992</bibRefCitation>
, figs 26–27). Based on these observations, we propose to transfer 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Patel" authorityYear="1988" box="[580,715,212,237]" class="Arachnida" family="Gnaphosidae" genus="Sergiolus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="17" pageNumber="2855" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="khodiarae">
<emphasis box="[580,715,212,237]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="2855">S. khodiarae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
to 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Westring" authorityYear="1874" box="[753,892,212,237]" class="Arachnida" family="Gnaphosidae" genus="Poecilochroa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="17" pageNumber="2855" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[753,892,212,237]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="2855">Poecilochroa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="17.[160,1155,142,271]" box="[192,373,246,271]" pageId="17" pageNumber="2855">
<emphasis box="[192,245,246,271]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="2855">Male</emphasis>
. Unknown.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="17.[160,1155,331,461]" box="[160,397,331,357]" pageId="17" pageNumber="2855">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[160,397,331,357]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="2855">Nomenclatural note</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="17.[160,1155,331,461]" pageId="17" pageNumber="2855">
Since the specific epithet of this species is based on the name of the 
<typeStatus box="[947,997,366,391]" pageId="17" pageNumber="2855">type</typeStatus>
locality (
<bibRefCitation author="Patel SK" pageId="17" pageNumber="2855" pagination="44 - 46" refId="ref7664" refString="Patel SK. 1988. A new species of spider of the genus: Sergiolus (Gnaphosidae) from India. Biol Bull India. 10: 44 - 46." type="journal article" year="1988">Patel 1988</bibRefCitation>
), the name is therefore proposed to be modified as 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Sankaran &amp; Caleb &amp; Sebastian" authorityYear="2021" baseAuthorityName="Patel" baseAuthorityYear="1988" box="[794,877,401,426]" class="Arachnida" family="Gnaphosidae" genus="Poecilochroa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="17" pageNumber="2855" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="khodiar">
<emphasis box="[794,877,401,426]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="2855">khodiar</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(considering it a noun in apposition), instead of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Patel" authorityYear="1988" box="[419,528,436,461]" class="Arachnida" family="Gnaphosidae" genus="Sergiolus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="17" pageNumber="2855" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="khodiarae">
<emphasis box="[419,528,436,461]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="2855">khodiarae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as mentioned in the original description.
</paragraph>
